					<a href="https://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/Eccl/9852?vers_inline=1"><img src="https://catholicbible.online/assets/img/para.jpg" alt="" /></a>					<a href="https://catholicbible.online/douay_rheims/OT/Eccl/9852?comments_open=1"><img src="https://catholicbible.online/assets/img/C-off.gif" alt="" /></a>				</div>
